responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "640307134359C43CA94D8FAC5C5962AE", "The Statue of Gom is a crude relic of the Age of Titans. The giants seem to think they have a divine connection like we. Their pea sized brains dreamed up a deity named Gom before the rise of the Aelans. This statue is one of the last known artifacts of this false god.")
